<br>
Where<br>
S = Skill<br>
T = Trivial<br>
C = Your chance of a successful combine.<br>
M = The point where your C maxes out at 95%<br>
<br>
C = (S-0.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> -(T-75)<br>
M = 95+0.8+T-75<br>
<br>
